      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a Vanos system overhaul and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral G-loads. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics with fresh bushings, providing precise turn-in and communicative feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this an ideal candidate for the spirited purist.",
